oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: George Thomas and Carl Dieckman perform Anniversary Blue Yodel -- Jimmie Rodgers Memorial Day - 1953-05-26 - Eddie Hill and Jim Evans excerpt
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: George Thomas (vocals, guitar) and Carl Dieckman (guitar) perform Jimmie Rodgers' Anniversary Blue Yodel, followed by an excerpt of Eddie Hill and Jim Evans talking on stage at the Jimmie Rodgers Memorial day, held in Meridian, Mississippi on May 26, 1953.
